title: Charly's All is Fair
description: Vegan catering specializing in cakes and baked goods. Kitchen is close to The Hague train station Laan van NOI. Relocated from The Hague in 2014. Delivers to The Hague, Voorburg, Leidschendam, and Nootdorp. For diner you have to stop by Charly's herself (need make arrangement).
